{"title":"攻击装置","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2545","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>给定一个01矩阵，其中你可以在0的位置放置攻击装置。每一个攻击装置（x,y）都可以按照“日”字攻击其周围的8个位置（x-1,y-2）,(x-2,y-1),(x+1,y-2),(x+2,y-1),(x-1,y+2),(x-2,y+1),(x+1,y+2),(x+2,y+1)</p>\n<p>求在装置互不攻击的情况下，最多可以放置多少个装置。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行一个整数N，表示矩阵大小为N*N。接下来N行每一行一个长度N的01串，表示矩阵。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个整数，表示在装置互不攻击的情况下最多可以放置多少个装置。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3<br>010<br>000<br>100</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>数据范围 <br>30%数据N&lt;=50<br>100%数据 N&lt;=200</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}